	<tr><td colspan="2" bgcolor="#666699" vAlign="TOP">
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Nope, just continue to kill everything in sight.  There's much speculation and conjecture about them being more frequent off of some mobs vs others.  However, I've done the epic twice now (yes, twice) and I can say with 99% certainty based off of my experience that it's completely random.  If you've got some pals, I'd say beg them to help you mow down mobs for an afternoon or more because the only real way to increase your chances is to increase the number of mobs you're killing.    Good Luck!</font></p>
	
